'''Rishi''' ({{lang-kn|ರಿಷಿ}}) is a 2005 Indian [[Kannada language|Kannada]] [[romance film]] directed and written by [[Prakash (film director)|Prakash]]. The film stars [[Shivarajkumar]], [[Vijay Raghavendra]], [[Radhika Kumaraswamy]] and [[Sindhu Tolani]] in the lead roles along with [[Srinath]] and [[Avinash]] in other prominent roles.<ref>[http://entertainment.oneindia.in/kannada/movies/rishi/cast-crew.html Cast & Crew]</ref> The score and soundtrack was by [[Gurukiran]] whose compositions were appreciated by critics and masses. The film eventually went on to become one of the hits of the year 2005.<ref>[http://www.chitraloka.com/movie-reviews/2807-kushi-review.html Khushi movie review]</ref> The film was remade in Telugu as ''[[Bangaru Babu (2009 film)|Bangaru Babu]]'' (2009) with [[Jagapathi Babu]].<ref>http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-features/tp-fridayreview/remake-of-a-family-drama/article656751.ece</ref>
